ver 0.1.1 - 2010-01-18 Krystian Szymukowicz  <http://www.cms-partner.pl/>

	* fixed bug with relative ext path in include
	
ver 0.1.0 - 2009-12-05 Krystian Szymukowicz  <http://www.cms-partner.pl/>

	* compatibility with tt_news 3.0.0
	* support for multilanguage
	* support for firstImageIsPreview and forceFirstImageIsPreview (but only for images from tt_news record)
	 
ver 0.0.4 - 2008-10-29 Krystian Szymukowicz  <http://www.cms-partner.pl/>

	* New tab "extra" with content elements can be now added to standard news. First standard etext and image is rendered - then content from tab "Extra".
	* Old text and images of tt_news can be now rendered using css_styled_content
	# Fixed: bug #1683, #1631, #1579, #1477

ver 0.0.3 - 2008-09-20 Krystian Szymukowicz  <http://www.cms-partner.pl/>

	* new EM configuration option
	- remove 'Link internal Page' 
	- remove 'Link internal Page'
	* new tt_news record Type 'Extended News'. 
	  Now editor can choose if he wants old editing or new one.


ver 0.0.2 - 2008-08-20 Krystian Szymukowicz  <http://www.cms-partner.pl/>

	* EM configuration option
	- more tabs
	- special tab for 'short' field
	- "hide" field reorganization for cleaner look
	* css for IRRE elements
	* image and text for LIST VIEW 
	

ver 0.0.1 - 2008-03-13 Georg Ringer  <http://www.ringer.it>

	* Initial release
